#  GTORIS — Smart Travel Planner

GTORIS is an AI-powered travel planning system that provides:
- Route optimization
- Cost & time estimation
- Transport comparison
- AI-based travel assistant (Ollama)

##  Features

-  Full India state & city selection
-  Real route mapping (OpenRouteService)
-  Local AI assistant (Ollama - no API required)
-  Smart travel insights

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- Streamlit
- Python
- Folium (Maps)
- OpenRouteService API
- Ollama (LLM)

